            <description sparkle:format="plain-text"><![CDATA[VoiceInk 1.70.37 — UI Modernization

- Liquid Glass mini recorder on macOS 26 (classic dark capsule on earlier systems)
- Native system materials across all cards and panels
- Resizable main window and standard macOS sidebar
- Dashboard Recent Activity: your last five transcriptions at a glance
- Cleaner History: hover-revealed selection, details inspector on selection
- Standard buttons and badges on model cards; Copy System Info moved to Settings > Diagnostics]]></description>
