            <description sparkle:format="plain-text"><![CDATA[VoiceInk 1.70.36

- Notarized Developer ID build with Sparkle auto-updates re-enabled
- FluidAudio upgraded to v0.15.4 (long-form accuracy fixes, download retries)
- Spoken punctuation ("comma", "open paren") and literal dictation tokens (/commands, @mentions)
- Lower-latency audio capture: lock-free realtime path with anti-aliased resampling
- Keyboard-layout-aware paste (no more input-source switching)]]></description>
